This note provides details about defined benefit and defined contribution plans we sponsor for our employees. The &#34;Pension and Other Post-Employment Benefit Plans&#34; section of Note 1: Summary of Significant Accounting Policies provides information about how we account for pension and other post-employment plans and benefits. 

