There were no insurance recoveries recorded during the year ended December 31, 2022. During the years ended December 31, 2021 and 2020 , we recorded insurance recoveries of $ 37 million and $ 8 million, respectively, related to our remediation efforts. The recoveries are attributable to our Wood Products segment and are recorded within &#8220;Product remediation recoveries&#8221; in our Consolidated Statement of Operations . 

